name: Maita 2 Door small
description: Upgrade your entertainment area with this sleek and functional Modern TV Stand in a rich walnut finish. Designed to blend effortlessly with a variety of interior styles, it features a clean, minimalist profile with two open shelves for media devices and two side cabinets for additional storage. The unit stands on elegant gold-tone metal legs, offering both style and stability. A rear cable management hole ensures your space stays neat and clutter-free.

name: Classic Panel Headboard (Double)
description: Elevate your bedroom decor with this timeless Classic Panel Headboard finished in rich African Wenge. Designed for durability and simplicity, this headboard features a wide central panel framed by sturdy vertical supports and a clean, straight-edged top. The wood grain texture enhances its natural elegance, making it a perfect fit for both modern and traditional interiors. Ideal for queen or double beds, this headboard brings warmth and sophistication to any room.
